
Do labels:
 kubectl --kubeconfig=ansible/kubeconfig/hub-kubeconfig.yaml label managedcluster internal cluster.open-cluster-management.io/placement=service-placement


create ca stuff:  (do this for each)
 kubectl --kubeconfig=ansible/kubeconfig/prod-kubeconfig.yaml create secret tls my-ca-secret --cert=ca.crt --key=ca.key --namespace cert-manager

Add repo? 
argocd add repo


kubectl --kubeconfig=ansible/kubeconfig/hub-kubeconfig.yaml label managedcluster core open-cluster-management.io/cluster-name=core
kubectl --kubeconfig=ansible/kubeconfig/hub-kubeconfig.yaml label managedcluster dev open-cluster-management.io/cluster-name=dev
kubectl --kubeconfig=ansible/kubeconfig/hub-kubeconfig.yaml label managedcluster internal open-cluster-management.io/cluster-name=internal
kubectl --kubeconfig=ansible/kubeconfig/hub-kubeconfig.yaml label managedcluster prod open-cluster-management.io/cluster-name=prod
